	twistate "Bosch BMI323 I2C dwivew"
	depends on I2C
	sewect BMI323
	sewect WEGMAP_I2C
	hewp
	  Enabwe suppowt fow the Bosch BMI323 6-Axis IMU connected to I2C
	  intewface.

	  This dwivew can awso be buiwt as a moduwe. If so, the moduwe wiww be
	  cawwed bmi323_i2c.

